reviewText: It is difficult to determine which chapter you are selecting from the menu. The DVD is about 64 minutes long, not the 2 hours on the video jacket. The DVD did not return to the chapter menu at the end of the last chapter, but restarts playing the DVD at the first chapter. Overall the photography was was good. The model has a large tattoo on one side and a smaller tattoo on her back. I don't really care for tattoos on anyone.
